TITLE: Data Source for FS Repository - Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This Terraform configuration defines a data source to fetch information about an Elasticsearch snapshot repository of type `fs`. It references the name of the `my_fs_repo` resource defined earlier in the configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/terraform-provider-elasticstack/blob/main/docs/data-sources/elasticsearch_snapshot_repository.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
data "elasticstack_elasticsearch_snapshot_repository" "my_fs_repo" {
  name = elasticstack_elasticsearch_snapshot_repository.my_fs_repo.name
}
```

