TITLE: Static Credentials Configuration Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to configure static credentials (username and password) for the Elastic Stack provider in Terraform. The `elasticsearch` block defines the connection details for authentication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/terraform-provider-elasticstack/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Terraform
CODE:
```
provider "elasticstack" {
  elasticsearch {
    username  = "elastic"
    password  = "changeme"
    endpoints = ["http://localhost:9200"]
  }
}
```

