TITLE: Handling Errors in Spaces API Call in Go
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates error handling during a Spaces API call in Kibana using Go. It checks for a non-nil error and, if the response body is not nil, it attempts to decode the error message and returns an error object. The error message is retrieved from error object.
