TITLE: Drop Processor Example Usage in Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `elasticstack_elasticsearch_ingest_processor_drop` data source to create a processor that drops documents where the `network_name` is 'Guest'. The processor is then used in an ingest pipeline.
