TITLE: Create Elasticsearch Index Terraform
DESCRIPTION: Creates an Elasticsearch index named `my-index` with specific mappings for `email`, `first_name`, and `last_name` fields. The `deletion_protection` attribute is set to false, allowing the index to be deleted.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/terraform-provider-elasticstack/blob/main/docs/data-sources/elasticsearch_enrich_policy.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
resource "elasticstack_elasticsearch_index" "my_index" {
  name = "my-index"

  mappings = jsonencode({
    properties = {
      email      = { type = "text" }
      first_name = { type = "text" }
      last_name  = { type = "text" }
    }
  })
  deletion_protection = false
}
```

